Interface Queue

All Known Implementing Classes:
LinkedQueue
public interface Queue

Queue provides an interface to a FIFO queue data structure. It stores Objects as to allow for generic usage among any application.

Since:
1.0
Version:
1.0
Author:
Tim Cheadle
